HEADWORD: Suwarrow
<hw>Su*war"row</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The giant cactus (<spn>Cereus giganteus</spn>); -- so named by the
Indians of Arizona. Called also <altname>saguaro</altname>.</def> <--
Saguaro is the most common now -->⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

